column1: # The January and February 1917 figure is an aggregate.
# The figures for October and November 1925 are adjusted from nearby stations and have been omitted.
# The figure for September 1933 is adjusted from nearby stations and has been omitted.
# The January 1940 figure is part estimated for snow and has been retained.
# The 1946 readings may be from a slightly different location, as the altitude is 100 ft higher.
